1
00:00:00,253 --> 00:00:03,875
"Fruit"

2
00:00:04,433 --> 00:00:08,180
(Episode 5: Before the Boundary)

3
00:00:12,933 --> 00:00:14,500
Have you seen the art teacher?

4
00:00:15,066 --> 00:00:16,466
No, why?

5
00:00:34,848 --> 00:00:36,900
Excuse me, is Miss Zhang Ronghua here?

6
00:00:36,900 --> 00:00:39,733
Zhang Ronghua? You mean the art teacher?

7
00:00:39,733 --> 00:00:42,066
She's on leave this week, she won't be at school.

8
00:00:43,400 --> 00:00:44,559
By the way,

9
00:00:45,600 --> 00:00:47,933
you'll be getting a new teacher soon.

10
00:00:47,933 --> 00:00:50,200
Miss Zhang Ronghua's contract has ended.

11
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:51,966
This is her last semester.

12
00:00:51,966 --> 00:00:54,766
This will be your new art teacher.

13
00:01:00,967 --> 00:01:02,900
What do you mean?

14
00:01:02,900 --> 00:01:05,366
Is she not coming back?

15
00:01:05,366 --> 00:01:07,266
Right.

16
00:01:07,266 --> 00:01:08,566
What's wrong?

17
00:01:08,566 --> 00:01:11,200
She should have told you, right?

18
00:01:16,200 --> 00:01:18,100
Don't overthink it.

19
00:01:18,100 --> 00:01:20,166
Focus on your studies.

20
00:01:20,166 --> 00:01:21,600
You're going to be seniors.

21
00:01:21,600 --> 00:01:24,433
Art students still need to study hard, right?

22
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:33,233
Okay... thank you, Miss.

23
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:57,761
Why?

24
00:02:01,046 --> 00:02:03,198
♪ What is the reason? ♪

25
00:02:03,198 --> 00:02:04,597
♪ You don't seem drawn ♪

26
00:02:04,597 --> 00:02:08,430
♪ To the surface of me ♪

27
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:12,373
♪ But to something deeper ♪

28
00:02:12,373 --> 00:02:17,963
♪ My soul beneath it all ♪

29
00:02:17,963 --> 00:02:20,088
♪ What is the reason? ♪

30
00:02:20,088 --> 00:02:24,648
♪ In your deep, quiet eyes ♪

31
00:02:24,648 --> 00:02:27,796
♪ Lies a hidden emotion ♪

32
00:02:27,796 --> 00:02:34,556
♪ As if trying to pierce through me ♪

33
00:02:35,133 --> 00:02:36,366
Did you forget?

34
00:02:38,933 --> 00:02:41,200
Or did you just not want to tell me?

35
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:33,500
It's not that I can't accept you leaving.

36
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:39,033
What I can't accept...

37
00:03:40,166 --> 00:03:44,466
is that you didn't even
give me a chance to say goodbye.

38
00:04:18,166 --> 00:04:19,766
Then why am I still drawing?

39
00:04:25,440 --> 00:04:26,827
There's no point at all.

40
00:04:31,300 --> 00:04:33,800
Everything that happened

41
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:37,066
is now nothing but memories.

42
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:41,200
It's the fruit of first love.

43
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:43,200
Unable to ripen,

44
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:46,000
and unable to be harvested.
